  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tamōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n73/mode/1up">70</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n74/mode/1up">71</ref>.</p>
      <p>i - ḷ. peyarccoṟ kālantōṉṟā, viṉaiccol lōṭokkum orukūṟallātaviṭattu. e - ṟu.</p>
<p>cāttaṉ, koṟṟaṉ, uṇṭal, tiṉṟal eṉak kālantōṉṟātu niṟṟalum, uṇṭāṉ, tiṉṟāṉ eṉat toḻiṉilaiyoṭṭuvaṉa kālantōṉṟi niṟṟaluṅ kaṇṭukoḷka.</p>
<p>uṇṭāṉ tiṉṟāṉ eṉṉun toṭakkattup paṭuttuc collappaṭum toḻiṟpeyar viṉaiccoṟpōlat tiṇaiyum pāluṅ kālamumutalāyiṉavaṟṟai viḷakki, aṉ āṉ mutalākiyavīṟṟavāy varutaliṉ, toḻinilaiyoṭṭumeṉṟār. oṭṭumeṉpatu uvamaccol.</p>
<p>peyarākiya nilaiyaiyuṭaiyatu peyarnilaiyeṉa aṉmoḻittokai.</p>
<p>peyar - poruḷ; toḻinilaiyumatu.</p>
<p>kālantōṉṟāveṉpaṉa orucollāyp peyarnilaik kiḷavi yeṉpataṟku muṭipāyiṉa.</p>
<p>payaṉilaikōṭalum urupēṟṟalumākiya peyarilakkaṇam īṇṭup peṟappaṭutaliṉ, avaṟṟōṭiyaiyak kālantōṉṟāmaiyākiya peyarilakkaṇamum īṇṭē kūṟiṉār. perumpāṉmaipaṟṟik kālantōṉṟāmai peyarilakkaṇamāyiṟṟu.	(9)</p>
    </body>
  </text>
